# Datasets and model artifacts never enter the repo. These need the `**/` prefix:
# a pattern containing a slash is anchored to this file's directory, so a bare
# `data/raw/` would match only at the root and miss `machine-learning/data/raw/`.
**/data/raw/
**/data/processed/
**/data/eval/
**/data/train/
**/data/val/
# Extracted feature vectors — derived from explicit corpora, never committed.
*.npz
artifacts/
.pytest_cache/
# Dev-time credentials. .env.example is tracked; .env never is.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
